<h2>The 7-Stage Workflow That Captures Trends</h2>
<p>Detection without a publishing workflow is just data hoarding. The teams that win at trend content compress the gap between signal and publish to under 72 hours. Here is the workflow we use.</p>
<h3>Stage 1: Configure Your Signal Sources</h3>
<p>Pick 3 to 5 signal sources. Do not try to monitor everything. Quality of signal beats volume of signal.</p>
<p>A balanced starting setup:</p>
